    "description": "An introduction to algorithms and applications of deep learning. The course helps students get hands-on experience of building deep learning models to solve practical tasks including image recognition, image generation, reinforcement learning, and language translation. Topics include: machine learning theory; optimization in deep learning; convolutional neural networks; recurrent neural networks; generative adversarial networks; reinforcement learning; self-driving vehicle.",
